### Health
GET http://localhost:8000/api/health

### Seed statuses (optional; seed.mjs covers this)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/statuses/seed

### Login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@skycrm.local",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### List leads (use token below)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/leads
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create lead
POST http://localhost:8000/api/leads
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "phone": "9999999999",
  "source": "Website",
  "city": "Hyderabad",
  "category": "BTech Admissions"
}

### Change status to Follow-Up
POST http://localhost:8000/api/leads/{{leadId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "statusName": "Follow-Up"
}